# UI Conventions

## Component Library

Use shadcn/ui components as the foundation. Import from `@/components/ui/`.

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Avoid inline styles
- Use `cn()` helper (from shadcn) for conditional classes
- Design tokens via Tailwind config (colors, spacing, fonts)

## Color Palette Direction

- Primary: teal / blue-green (trustworthy, calm)
- Background: light / near-white
- Cards: white with subtle border or shadow
- Status colors: green (complete), amber (in progress), gray (not started), red (flagged/blocked)
- Text: dark gray, not pure black

## Layout

- Mobile-first responsive
- Consistent padding and spacing using Tailwind scale

## Checklist UI Patterns

- Checkboxes for items (not toggle switches)
- Strikethrough or muted style for completed items
- Progress bars or percentage badges per section
- Section cards with expand/collapse
- Status badges: Not started, In progress, Complete, Skipped

## Accessibility

- Semantic HTML (headings, lists, buttons)
- Keyboard navigable
- Sufficient color contrast
- ARIA labels where needed
